fields.name: Naruto
fields.description: A young ninja named Naruto Uzumaki aspires to become the Hokage, the leader of his village, while facing challenges and enemies along the way.

fields.name: Bleach
fields.description: Ichigo Kurosaki, a teenager with the ability to see ghosts, gains the power of a Soul Reaper and must defend humans from evil spirits and guide departed souls to the afterlife.

fields.name: OnePiece
fields.description: Monkey D. Luffy sets out on a journey to become the Pirate King, recruiting a diverse crew and facing powerful enemies along the way in search of the ultimate treasure, the One Piece.

fields.name: AttackOnTitan
fields.description: In a world where humanity lives within a walled city to protect itself from man-eating Titans, Eren Yeager and his friends join the Survey Corps to fight back and uncover the secrets of their world.

fields.name: FullmetalAlchemist
fields.description: In a world where alchemy is a powerful science, brothers Edward and Alphonse Elric search for the Philosopher's Stone to restore their bodies after a failed attempt to bring their mother back to life.

fields.name: DeathNote
fields.description: A high school student named Light Yagami finds a mysterious notebook that grants him the power to kill anyone whose name he writes in it, and begins a dangerous game of cat-and-mouse with a master detective trying to stop him.

fields.name: BreakingBad
fields.description: A high school chemistry teacher turns to making and selling methamphetamine in order to secure his family's financial future, while navigating the dangers of the criminal underworld.

fields.name: GameOfThrones
fields.description: In the Seven Kingdoms of Westeros, various families and factions fight for control of the Iron Throne and the ultimate power over the realm.

fields.name: TheSopranos
fields.description: A New Jersey mob boss tries to balance his family life and criminal empire, while dealing with mental health issues and the changing landscape of organized crime.

fields.name: TheWire
fields.description: In Baltimore, law enforcement, drug dealers, and politicians navigate a complex and often corrupt system, revealing the interconnectedness of power and crime in modern society.

fields.name: TheOffice
fields.description: A mockumentary-style sitcom follows the daily lives of employees at a Scranton, Pennsylvania paper company, capturing the humor and heart of office culture.

fields.name: Friends
fields.description: A group of six friends in New York City navigate their careers, relationships, and personal struggles while supporting each other through it all.

fields.name: Chernobyl
fields.description: Based on the true events of the 1986 nuclear disaster in Ukraine, this miniseries explores the human cost and political fallout of the worst nuclear accident in history.

fields.name: Pulp
fields.description: A pair of hit men, a boxer, a gangster's wife, and a pair of diner bandits interact with each other in various ways during a crime-filled Los Angeles day.

fields.name: Godfather
fields.description: The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant son.

fields.name: Shawshank
fields.description: Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.

fields.name: Fight
fields.description: An insomniac office worker and a devil-may-care soap maker form an underground fight club that evolves into much more.

fields.name: Schindler's
fields.description: In German-occupied Poland during World War II, industrialist Oskar Schindler gradually becomes concerned for his Jewish workforce after witnessing their persecution by the Nazis.

fields.name: Lord
fields.description: A meek hobbit of the Shire and eight companions set out on a journey to Mount Doom to destroy the One Ring and the dark lord Sauron.

fields.name: Dark
fields.description: A family saga with a supernatural twist, set in a German town, where the disappearance of two young children exposes the relationships among four families.
